# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s34_e0760be2:

    # "Drenched in sweat, I gasp to life and hack the sand out of my mouth."
    "Empapada en sudor, jadeo al volver a la vida y expulso la arena de mi boca."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s34_acfcf453:

    # "Memories from the night before start flooding back as I choke down a lump in my throat."
    "Los recuerdos de la noche anterior empiezan a inundarme mientras trago un nudo en la garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s34_e3f3955d:

    # "The desert, the tape, the stars—"
    "El desierto, la cinta, las estrellas..."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s34_56b929f4:

    # Amber "Marina!"
    Amber "Марина!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s34_47b64674:

    # "My head snaps to the sky. The sun is already a quarter of a way done with its cycle."
    "Giro la cabeza hacia el cielo. El sol ya ha completado una cuarta parte de su ciclo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s34_efbf5792:

    # "Soon, if it already hasn’t, the taxi will pick up Marina and I’ll never see her again."
    "Pronto, si no lo ha hecho ya, el taxi recogerá a Marina y nunca volveré a verla."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s34_b475d712:

    # "All because I couldn’t let myself trust Marina."
    "Todo porque no pude permitirme confiar en Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s34_d0cbde77:

    # Amber "Dammit!"
    Amber "Черт!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s34_f050897a:

    # "I slam my fists down, kicking up a pitiful plume of sand."
    "Golpeo con los puños, levantando una lastimosa nube de arena."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s34_a28c2c53:

    # "Even if I ran, I’d never be able to make it in time."
    "Incluso si corriera, nunca llegaría a tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s34_6e287b00:

    # "If only I had the motorhome."
    "Si tan solo tuviera la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s34_8e320f65:

    # "Wait…"
    "Espera..."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s34_c4f668cc:

    # Amber "Mariah!"
    Amber "Мария!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s34_14256cd9:

    # "There’s a chance they still might be camped out nearby."
    "Hay una posibilidad de que todavía estén acampando cerca."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s34_2cd86556:

    # "Wiping the tears from my eyes, I spring to my feet and sprint in the direction of their motorhome, leaving the half-buried cassette behind me."
    "Secándome las lágrimas de los ojos, me pongo de pie de un salto y corro en dirección a su casa rodante, dejando atrás el cassette medio enterrado."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s34_30011599:

    # "Please still be there, please still be there."
    "Por favor, que sigan ahí, por favor, que sigan ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s34_6bee0512:

    # "Sure enough, it’s right where it was last night."
    "Efectivamente, está justo donde estaba anoche."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s34_c43b4919:

    # "I run up and pound on the door, knocking harder and louder until someone answers."
    "Corro y golpeo la puerta, llamando más fuerte y más alto hasta que alguien responde."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s34_04bca01c:

    # "Looking up with wide eyes, Tess opens the door and stares at me."
    "Levantando la vista con los ojos muy abiertos, Tess abre la puerta y me mira fijamente."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s34_e5b7fe02:

    # Amber "Tess! Is Mariah here?"
    Amber "Тесс! Мария здесь?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s34_80f98f2f:

    # Joseph "Amber?"
    Joseph "Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s34_4d46e486:

    # "Joe slinks off the couch and joins Tess at the door."
    "Joe se desliza del sofá y se une a Tess en la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:154
translate spanish hwb_s34_f9e967d1:

    # Joseph "Sheesh, you’re a wreck. Everything okay?"
    Joseph "Воу, ты выглядишь хреново. Все в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s34_b54bf3a8:

    # Amber "Quick, the time!"
    Amber "Быстрее у меня нет времени!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s34_19cebbb2:

    # Joseph "Eh?"
    Joseph "М?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:166
translate spanish hwb_s34_e1d0796d:

    # Amber "The time! What time is it?"
    Amber "Время! Сколько время?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s34_c762ff5f:

    # Joseph "Uh…"
    Joseph "Эм…"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s34_ab5c256f:

    # "He looks to the invisible watch on his wrist, then switches between all the walls before Tess digs around in her shorts and hands him a chained pocket watch."
    "Mira el reloj invisible en su muñeca, luego cambia entre todas las paredes hasta que Tess hurga en sus pantalones cortos y le entrega un reloj de bolsillo con cadena."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s34_bbabcf9f:

    # Joseph "Ten o'clock, apparently."
    Joseph "Ровно десять."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s34_03fcde8b:

    # "He turns to Tess."
    "Se vuelve hacia Tess."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s34_57d7496b:

    # Joseph "When did you start carrying this around?"
    Joseph "С каких пор ты начала носить эту штуку с собой?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s34_a6a6b4bf:

    # Mariah "{size=+10}WHY THE HELL’S IT SO FRIGGIN’ LOUD?{/size}" with hpunch
    Mariah "{size=+10}КАКОГО ЧЕРТА ЗДЕСЬ ТАК ГРОМКО?{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s34_981b9791:

    # "A bottle comes hurdling towards Joe, but he ducks at the last second, letting it shatter across the wall."
    "Una botella sale volando hacia Joe, pero él se agacha en el último segundo, dejando que se estrelle contra la pared."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s34_2091e0b0:

    # Joseph "Oh yeah. She smashed the last one."
    Joseph "Зашибись. Она разбила последнюю."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s34_a54c231b:

    # Amber "Fifteen minutes! There’s still time!"
    Amber "Пятнадцать минут! Время еще есть!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s34_147dc8d4:

    # Joseph "Woah, slow down a sec. Time for what?"
    Joseph "Воу, притормози. Пятнадцать минут до чего?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s34_953196a1:

    # Amber "I know this is short notice, but I need a ride!"
    Amber "Я знаю, времени мало, но мне срочно надо ехать!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:220
translate spanish hwb_s34_a5b7c376:

    # Joseph "A ride? Now?"
    Joseph "Ехать? Сейчас?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s34_b490dfbb:

    # Mariah "{size=+10}I SAID SHUT THE HELL UP!{/size}" with hpunch
    Mariah "{size=+10}Я КАЖЕТСЯ ВЕЛЕЛА ТЕБЕ ЗАТКНУТЬСЯ НАХРЕН!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s34_df253102:

    # "Another bottle comes flying towards him, but this time Tess hops and snatches it out of the air."
    "Otra botella viene volando hacia él, pero esta vez Tess salta y la atrapa en el aire."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s34_3ad04daf:

    # "He looks across the room then back to me."
    "Mira al otro lado de la habitación y luego de vuelta a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s34_d6ad3c22:

    # Joseph "Now’s probably not the best time."
    Joseph "Сейчас не лучшее время для этого."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s34_f7368963:

    # Tess "Sis’ hangovers are lethal."
    Tess "У сестренки сильное похмелье."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s34_9f919ea7:

    # Amber "No! We need to leave now!"
    Amber "Нет! Нам надо ехать сейчас!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s34_1ae408be:

    # Mariah "{size=+10}DO YOU NOT REMEMBER WHAT I SAID I’D DO WITH THE JUMPER CABLES THE NEXT TIME YOU—{/size}" with hpunch
    Mariah "{size=+10}ТЫ УЖЕ ЗАБЫЛ ЧТО Я ОБЕЩАЛА СДЕЛАТЬ С КАБЕЛЬНЫМИ ПЕРЕМЫЧКАМИ ЕСЛИ ТЫ—{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s34_bfe6c85f:

    # "Nursing her forehead and lifting up another bottle, Mariah stomps over, only to freeze once she sees me."
    "Sosteniéndose la frente y levantando otra botella, Mariah se acerca pisando fuerte, solo para congelarse al verme."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s34_0bec5367:

    # Amber "Mariah! I need a ride!"
    Amber "Мария! Мне нужно одолжить твой фургон!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:303
translate spanish hwb_s34_e69d80e7:

    # Amber "Please! You were right! I made a big mistake and if I’m not back at our hotel in fifteen I’ll never see Marina again!"
    Amber "Пожалуйста! Ты была права! Я сделала большую ошибку и если я не вернусь в отель через пятнадцать минут, я больше никогда не увижу Марину!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s34_02f944b1:

    # "The motorhome falls silent, all eyes on Mariah."
    "La casa rodante queda en silencio, todas las miradas puestas en Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s34_6bc08e49:

    # "Her face is blank, unreadable compared to all the crazy looking scowls she usually wears."
    "Su rostro está en blanco, ilegible en comparación con todos los ceños fruncidos y locos que suele poner."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s34_237e7480:

    # "Finally, she speaks."
    "Finalmente, habla."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s34_525a9b57:

    # Mariah "Alright. Let her in."
    Mariah "Хорошо. Впустите ее."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s34_c403ae1a:

    # Joseph "I’m really sorry, but you know how she—wait."
    Joseph "Извини конечно, но ты знаешь как она... Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s34_c038f776:

    # Joseph "For real?"
    Joseph "Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s34_50091fb8:

    # "Mariah closes her eyes and takes a deep, long breath."
    "Mariah cierra los ojos y toma una respiración larga y profunda."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s34_fbd26c44:

    # Mariah "Before I change my mind."
    Mariah "Пока я не передумала."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s34_1d44caa4:

    # "Joe and Tess shoot each other surprised glances, then shrug."
    "Joe y Tess intercambian miradas sorprendidas, luego se encogen de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s34_809f7c46:

    # Joseph "Well what do you know? Miracles actually do happen."
    Joseph "Что это было? Похоже, чудеса действительно случаются."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s34_d779fda0:

    # Tess "The desert heat has thawed her icy heart."
    Tess "Тепло пустыни разморозило ее холодное сердце."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s34_c1440992:

    # Mariah "Yeah, yeah. Just shut up and get ready."
    Mariah "Да, да. Просто заткнитесь и будьте готовы."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s34_37cd9b16:

    # "I hop in. The other two scurry around and batten down the hatches, strapping shut all the cupboards and shelves."
    "Me subo. Los otros dos corretean y aseguran las escotillas, cerrando con correas todos los armarios y estantes."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:388
translate spanish hwb_s34_e80b689f:

    # "Grabbing her bandanna, Mariah ties it around her head while I shuffle around and try to spit out a thank you."
    "Agarrando su pañuelo, Mariah se lo ata alrededor de la cabeza mientras yo me muevo nerviosa e intento balbucear un agradecimiento."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s34_3cafc5f7:

    # Amber "So, uh, I should probab—"
    Amber "Наверно мне сто—"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s34_a5283751:

    # Joseph "We’re all set! I’ll take the wheel!"
    Joseph "Мы все готовы! Я поведу!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s34_7a496f3b:

    # "Joe rushes past us with the keys, but Mariah trips him and snags them from his hand."
    "Joe pasa corriendo a nuestro lado con las llaves, pero Mariah le hace una zancadilla y se las arrebata de la mano."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s34_f3bcea52:

    # Mariah "No way! You drive like an old man. {i}I’ll{/i} drive."
    Mariah "Ну уж нет! Ты водишь как старик. {i}Я{/i} поведу."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s34_351fca09:

    # Joseph "No, I drive like a normal person. You just happen to drive like a maniac. Besides, you’re hungover!"
    Joseph "Нет, я вожу как нормальные люди, а ты водишь как безбашенный маньяк. Кроме того, у тебя похмелье!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s34_46c15bd5:

    # Mariah "It’ll be fine! Just c’mon!"
    Mariah "Да все нормально! Поехали уже!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s34_fd564163:

    # "They both dart over to the front seats and the RV roars to life."
    "Ambas corren hacia los asientos delanteros y la casa rodante ruge a la vida."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s34_9b3ed198:

    # Mariah "Tess! Hair of the dog!"
    Mariah "Тесс! Опохмел!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s34_0ba5a24b:

    # "Tess nods and runs to the fridge, grabbing a bottle that looks a lot like the ones from last night, except this one has a picture of the devil on it."
    "Tess asiente y corre al refrigerador, agarrando una botella que se parece mucho a las de anoche, excepto que esta tiene una imagen del diablo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s34_bdb1f5eb:

    # "She tosses it over to her sister, who showcases the same catching talent as her."
    "Se la lanza a su hermana, quien demuestra el mismo talento para atrapar que ella."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s34_8b65b502:

    # Mariah "Now that’s what I’m talking about!"
    Mariah "Теперь то что надо!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s34_51bee664:

    # "Slamming the bottle in the cup holder, Mariah sticks her head out the window and backs up the motorhome."
    "Golpeando la botella en el portavasos, Mariah saca la cabeza por la ventana y retrocede la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s34_036a7c86:

    # "Joe shakes his head, replacing the devil’s brew with a nearby water bottle while she isn’t looking."
    "Joe niega con la cabeza, reemplazando el brebaje del diablo con una botella de agua cercana mientras ella no mira."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s34_47ad94d6:

    # Joseph "You’re going to need to hang on tight, by the way."
    Joseph "Кстасти, советую держаться покрепче."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s34_a65747b5:

    # Amber "Huh? Why?"
    Amber "М? Это еще почему?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s34_0a1650e6:

    # "My question is immediately answered, as I’m flung against the couch. Tess’ small frame crashes into me."
    "Mi pregunta se responde de inmediato, cuando soy lanzada contra el sofá. La pequeña figura de Tess choca contra mí."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s34_64c92e36:

    # Tess "It doesn’t hurt as much if you relax your muscles."
    Tess "Становится не особо больно, если расслабляешь мускулы."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s34_c1550433:

    # "The RV speeds forward. The license plate wind chime dings in chaotic disunion as the bottles and cans roll across the floor, clanging together whenever they meet."
    "La casa rodante acelera hacia adelante. El móvil de matrículas suena en caótica discordia mientras las botellas y latas ruedan por el piso, chocando entre sí cada vez que se encuentran."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:482
translate spanish hwb_s34_65638873:

    # "Even the table is seesawing back and forth."
    "Hasta la mesa se balancea de un lado a otro."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s34_25714e75:

    # "I look out the window. Mariah flies onto the road, cutting off an entire lane of cars."
    "Miro por la ventana. Mariah se lanza a la carretera, cortando un carril entero de autos."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:502
translate spanish hwb_s34_807cf1b5:

    # "The RV hits the ground and bounces. I manage to keep my head from bashing the cot above me, but Tess lets herself get tossed around, rolling across the floor with the trash." with vpunch
    "Трейлер подскакивает на кочках. Мне удается не удариться головой о раскладушку, но Тесс так и летит на пол, перекатываясь по нему вместе с бутылками, которые там валялись." with vpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s34_e42378ed:

    # Mariah "So where exactly am I going?"
    Mariah "Куда конкретно мне ехать?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:508
translate spanish hwb_s34_b4e801c2:

    # Amber "The hotel downtown! You’d have to be stupid to miss it!"
    Amber "Центральный отель! Нужно быть умственно отсталым, чтобы его пропустить!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:512
translate spanish hwb_s34_25974064:

    # Joseph "Remember who you’re talking to here."
    Joseph "Помни с кем ты говоришь."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s34_9938d7b9:

    # Mariah "Hotel? You didn’t spend any of my treasure on that, did you?"
    Mariah "Отель? Вы же не растратили мой клад?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s34_357537e3:

    # "Mariah glares back at me, oblivious to everything on the other side of the windshield."
    "Mariah me devuelve una mirada furiosa, ajena a todo lo que está al otro lado del parabrisas."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:523
translate spanish hwb_s34_a4f29671:

    # Amber "I might’ve used a nugget to bribe the manager…"
    Amber "Совсем чуть-чуть, мы отдали самородок, чтобы расплатиться с менеджером…"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s34_6253992a:

    # Mariah "WHAT? I’ll kill you!" with hpunch
    Mariah "ЧТО? Я убью тебя!" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s34_3f925a78:

    # Joseph "Save the cat fight for later! There are more important things to focus on right now—like the road!"
    Joseph "Оставь разборки на потом! В данный момент есть более важные вещи, на которых было бы неплохо сосредоточится - например дорога!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:536
translate spanish hwb_s34_dc3292d4:

    # Mariah "The road will always be there, Joe! My treasure won’t!"
    Mariah "Дорога всегда будет на месте, Джо! А мой клад нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:540
translate spanish hwb_s34_95b04207:

    # Joseph "The treasure or our lives?"
    Joseph "Клад важнее наших жизней?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:544
translate spanish hwb_s34_8351bcc4:

    # "I think everyone here already knows the answer to that one."
    "Creo que todos aquí ya saben la respuesta a esa."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:546
translate spanish hwb_s34_795789ae:

    # Mariah "Pffft. I had Tess do the math. The treasure is worth way more than any of yo—"
    Mariah "Пффф. Обычно Тесс, ведет всю бухгалтерию. Но и так ясно, сокровище стоит куда больше, чем каждый из ва-"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:550
translate spanish hwb_s34_c608bfc9:

    # Amber "Watch out!"
    Amber "Берегись!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:556
translate spanish hwb_s34_87638f38:

    # "A big rig comes speeding towards us, blasting its deafening horn." with hpunch
    "Огромная махина мчится прямо на нас, издавая оглушительные гудки." with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:558
translate spanish hwb_s34_240672ca:

    # "At the last second, Mariah swerves back into her lane as the truck barrels past us."
    "En el último segundo, Mariah gira de vuelta a su carril mientras el camión pasa rugiendo a nuestro lado."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:560
translate spanish hwb_s34_fc93cac3:

    # "The motorhome hits a bump and bounces up again."
    "La casa rodante golpea un bache y rebota de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:568
translate spanish hwb_s34_e3b5dc77:

    # "Unprepared, poor Joe’s head hits the ceiling, knocking the light from his eyes. If I squint hard enough I can even see his soul drifting away from his body."
    "Desprevenido, el pobre Joe golpea su cabeza contra el techo, apagando la luz de sus ojos. Si entrecierro lo suficiente, hasta puedo ver su alma alejándose de su cuerpo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s34_90a8adcc:

    # Tess "Sis, I think Joey’s dead."
    Tess "Сестренка, у нас потери. Джо мертв."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:576
translate spanish hwb_s34_f2ec629e:

    # Mariah "About damn time! He was getting annoying!"
    Mariah "Как раз вовремя! Он уже начинал раздражать!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:580
translate spanish hwb_s34_00c3da93:

    # "Tess salutes her fallen comrade."
    "Tess saluda a su camarada caído."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:582
translate spanish hwb_s34_7ab1d2b1:

    # "It’s always the sane ones who dies first."
    "Siempre son los cuerdos los que mueren primero."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:584
translate spanish hwb_s34_0f385d3c:

    # "We zoom past the town’s welcoming center. It’s not far at all now."
    "Pasamos zumbando por el centro de bienvenida del pueblo. Ya no queda mucho."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:588
translate spanish hwb_s34_85303505:

    # Amber "Tess, what time is it?"
    Amber "Тесс, сколько время?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:592
translate spanish hwb_s34_c85d746a:

    # Tess "10:12."
    Tess "10:12."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:594
translate spanish hwb_s34_b1c8bdd7:

    # "I grit my teeth and glare out the window."
    "Aprieto los dientes y miro fijamente por la ventana."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:596
translate spanish hwb_s34_bfe9a3e5:

    # "Please still be there."
    "Por favor, que todavía esté allí."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:598
translate spanish hwb_s34_444b603d:

    # "Downtown comes into view, the strip of familiar stores and restaurants start forming."
    "El centro aparece a la vista, la hilera de tiendas y restaurantes familiares comienza a formarse."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:600
translate spanish hwb_s34_0d0bfb12:

    # "Mariah races down the street, ignoring all traffic lights and pedestrians as people leap out of the way and cars brake into other lanes."
    "Mariah corre por la calle, ignorando todos los semáforos y peatones mientras la gente salta para apartarse y los autos frenan hacia otros carriles."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:604
translate spanish hwb_s34_97420afb:

    # Amber "We’re almost there! Get ready!"
    Amber "Мы почти на месте! Приготовься!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:608
translate spanish hwb_s34_cace5c9a:

    # "The hotel looms just up ahead. Through the windshield I can see Marina holding on to a small suitcase as she prepares to step into the cab."
    "El hotel se alza justo adelante. A través del parabrisas, veo a Marina sosteniendo una maleta pequeña mientras se prepara para subir al taxi."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:615
translate spanish hwb_s34_288af047:

    # "I leap to the door and swing it open. Wind rushes through my hair. The motorhome is slowing down, but I don’t care."
    "Salto hacia la puerta y la abro de golpe. El viento agita mi cabello. La casa rodante está frenando, pero no me importa."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:617
translate spanish hwb_s34_9608ef98:

    # Mariah "The hell are you doi—"
    Mariah "Какого черта ты твор—"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:643
translate spanish hwb_s34_1dc0a5df:

    # "I launch myself onto the street, tumbling across the burning concrete as the road tears against my skin."
    "Me lanzo a la calle, rodando sobre el concreto ardiente mientras el pavimento raspa mi piel."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s34_e450e52e:

    # "Immediately, I spring back up and dart towards Marina."
    "De inmediato, me levanto de un salto y corro hacia Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:654
translate spanish hwb_s34_61dd3a19:

    # "Mariah screeches to a halt in the middle of the street, blocking anyone from driving through. The three of them hop out, Joe clutching his head as he stumbles out the door."
    "Mariah frena en seco en medio de la calle, bloqueando el paso a cualquiera. Los tres saltan del vehículo, Joe agarrándose la cabeza mientras sale tambaleándose por la puerta."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s34_58d7b922:

    # Marina "A-Amber?"
    Marina "Э-эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:680
translate spanish hwb_s34_4211b659:

    # "Before she can get another word, I grab her by the waist and throw my lips against hers."
    "Antes de que pueda decir otra palabra, la tomo por la cintura y pego mis labios contra los suyos."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:684
translate spanish hwb_s34_e76a7984:

    # "She pulls herself away and glares at me through her puffy, red eyes."
    "Se aparta y me fulmina con la mirada a través de sus ojos hinchados y enrojecidos."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:686
translate spanish hwb_s34_a56b7bad:

    # "I plant my hands on her shoulders and steady myself as tears stream down my face."
    "Apoyo las manos en sus hombros y me estabilizo mientras las lágrimas me corren por el rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:688
translate spanish hwb_s34_4338e6de:

    # Amber "I’m sorry, I’m so sorry."
    Amber "Прости меня, прости пожалуйста."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:690
translate spanish hwb_s34_b4278bef:

    # "Marina freezes, then she slowly softens from a glare to a strain. I catch a lump building her throat, too."
    "Marina se congela, luego su mirada se suaviza lentamente de furia a tensión. También noto un nudo formándose en su garganta."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:694
translate spanish hwb_s34_061aef20:

    # Marina "I thought you weren’t coming back…"
    Marina "Я думала ты не вернешься…"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:696
translate spanish hwb_s34_92fa6741:

    # Amber "I know, I know. I was such a bitch."
    Amber "Я знаю, знаю. Я вела себя как последняя сука."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:698
translate spanish hwb_s34_c91a7abb:

    # Amber "I didn’t mean any of it. I love you so much, I just didn’t want to hurt you."
    Amber "Я была не права. Я сильно тебя люблю, я не хотела тебя обижать."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:700
translate spanish hwb_s34_2682791e:

    # Marina "Wh-What? How could you ever hurt me?"
    Marina "Чт-что? Разве ты могла меня обидеть?"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:702
translate spanish hwb_s34_b26d42a7:

    # Amber "I was scared…"
    Amber "Я так боялась…"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:704
translate spanish hwb_s34_59613d7d:

    # "The tears don’t stop. The crying gets louder."
    "Las lágrimas no cesan. El llanto se vuelve más fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:706
translate spanish hwb_s34_f94b54f9:

    # Amber "I was afraid I was using you because I didn’t have Gramps anymore, I lost my family."
    Amber "Я боялась, что использую тебя потому, что дедушки больше нет и я потеряла свою семью."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:708
translate spanish hwb_s34_0288be42:

    # Amber "I always wanted to help you, but I think I might be the one who really needs help."
    Amber "Я всегда хотела помочь тебе, но я думаю что мне самой нужна помощь."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:712
translate spanish hwb_s34_e5d457b6:

    # "Marina can’t hold it back any longer and starts bawling in my arms, hugging me as tight as she possibly can."
    "Marina ya no puede contenerlo más y rompe a llorar en mis brazos, abrazándome tan fuerte como puede."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:716
translate spanish hwb_s34_eb2fc47d:

    # Marina "Dummy, I’m your new family! I don’t care if you use me, I love you!"
    Marina "Глупышка, я твоя новая семья! И мне все равно используешь ли ты меня, я люблю тебя!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:718
translate spanish hwb_s34_78e30b1c:

    # Amber "I love you, too!"
    Amber "Я тоже тебя люблю!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:722
translate spanish hwb_s34_9864cd79:

    # "This time we both move in for the kiss, two blubbering idiots trying to prove just how much the other means."
    "Esta vez ambas nos acercamos para el beso, dos idiotas llorando que intentan demostrar cuánto significa la otra."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:724
translate spanish hwb_s34_22f99b6e:

    # "I’m not sure if it’s her tears I’m tasting or mine, but I can still make out the soft sweetness of her lips regardless."
    "No estoy segura si son sus lágrimas o las mías las que saboreo, pero aún así puedo percibir la suave dulzura de sus labios."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s34_9b6e034d:

    # "It’s funny."
    "Es curioso."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:728
translate spanish hwb_s34_70f80e28:

    # "This entire time, I thought I was the nucleus of it all."
    "Todo este tiempo, pensé que yo era el núcleo de todo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:730
translate spanish hwb_s34_0bfef031:

    # "That I was the one helping her—or using her."
    "Que yo era quien la ayudaba—o la usaba."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:732
translate spanish hwb_s34_556fe15e:

    # "But as cheesy as it sounds, I think Marina has always been the one helping me. From the very beginning."
    "Pero por cursi que suene, creo que Marina siempre ha sido quien me ha ayudado a mí. Desde el principio."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:736
translate spanish hwb_s34_bae72e5b:

    # "Through the kissing, I catch a glimpse of the trio, Joe covering Tess’ eyes as he slips Mariah a bill."
    "A través del beso, vislumbro al trío: Joe tapándole los ojos a Tess mientras le pasa un billete a Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:790
translate spanish hwb_s34_c0209fae:

    # "We manage to compose ourselves enough to pull each other away, but we never let go of the other’s hand."
    "Logramos recomponernos lo suficiente para separarnos, pero nunca soltamos la mano de la otra."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:792
translate spanish hwb_s34_bfbbb7b2:

    # "Rolling her eyes, Mariah unties her bandanna and tosses it to me."
    "Rodando los ojos, Mariah se desata el pañuelo y me lo lanza."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:798
translate spanish hwb_s34_0df57ad7:

    # Mariah "You both look disgusting. Here."
    Mariah "Вы обе выглядите отвратительно. Вот."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:803
translate spanish hwb_s34_f15aa11a:

    # Amber "Heh. Thanks."
    Amber "Хах. Спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:815
translate spanish hwb_s34_710b45c3:

    # "I wipe away as many of my tears as I can before passing it along to Marina, who blows into it like a trumpet." with hpunch
    "Я вытираю мокрые от слез щеки перед тем, как передать бандану Марине, которая громко сморкается в нее со звуками, напоминающими духовой инструмент." with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:819
translate spanish hwb_s34_4c41e6ac:

    # "She sniffs, her nose red and tears still leaking out, then hands the drenched cloth back to Mariah, who gives it to Joe."
    "Ella solloza, con la nariz roja y lágrimas aún escapándose, luego le devuelve el paño empapado a Mariah, quien se lo da a Joe."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:824
translate spanish hwb_s34_9a3b465b:

    # "He cringes as he dangles it from his fingers."
    "Él hace una mueca mientras lo sostiene con los dedos."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:828
translate spanish hwb_s34_7c217a8f:

    # Marina "Hi, guys."
    Marina "Привет ребята."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:836
translate spanish hwb_s34_50943fb0:

    # "{color=#c9c9c9}Tess{/color}, {color=#FF9201}Joseph{/color}, and {color=#ffdab3}Mariah{/color}" "Hi."
    JoeTessMariah "Привет."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:838
translate spanish hwb_s34_7076bc00:

    # Amber "Thanks, you three. I mean it. Especially you, Mariah."
    Amber "Спасибо вам троим. Всем вам. Особенно тебе, Мария."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:844
translate spanish hwb_s34_fa06fa04:

    # "For a moment, Mariah lowers her guard and {i}almost{/i} smirks, then remembers it’s just not her style."
    "Por un momento, Mariah baja la guardia y {i}casi{/i} esboza una sonrisa, luego recuerda que simplemente no es su estilo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:846
translate spanish hwb_s34_07a5c7df:

    # Mariah "Whatever. That doesn’t make us cool or anything. I still despise you."
    Mariah "Пофигу. Это не делает нас друзьями. Я все еще презираю тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:850
translate spanish hwb_s34_ad925bce:

    # Tess "It’s true."
    Tess "Это так."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:854
translate spanish hwb_s34_bd04fd42:

    # Joseph "Yeah, she hates your guts."
    Joseph "Да, она тебя ненавидит."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:858
translate spanish hwb_s34_36c98afc:

    # Amber "Wouldn’t have it any other way."
    Amber "А мне другого и не надо."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:862
translate spanish hwb_s34_f1130fb4:

    # "Marina giggles and I bring her in closer, then suddenly, I remember something."
    "Marina ríe y la acerco más, entonces, de repente, recuerdo algo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:866
translate spanish hwb_s34_1d72b5b3:

    # Amber "Oh!"
    Amber "О!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:874
translate spanish hwb_s34_099de754:

    # "I bend over and dig through Marina’s suitcase, bringing out a single gold nugget and passing it to Mariah."
    "Me inclino y hurgo en la maleta de Marina, sacando una sola pepita de oro y pasándosela a Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:880
translate spanish hwb_s34_30632433:

    # Amber "Figured yours was getting lonely."
    Amber "Я подумала, что твоему будет одиноко."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:889
translate spanish hwb_s34_8788430e:

    # "Mariah stares at her hand, the other two gathering around her."
    "Mariah mira su mano, mientras los otros dos se reúnen a su alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:893
translate spanish hwb_s34_b0d822f1:

    # Joseph "How about that? You ended up getting the treasure after all, Mariah!"
    Joseph "Ну что? В конце концов ты получила  свое сокровище, Мария!"

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:897
translate spanish hwb_s34_25bfe666:

    # Tess "It seems bigger than the one we have."
    Tess "Этот выглядит больше чем наш."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:899
translate spanish hwb_s34_76a2d03d:

    # "Finally defeated, Mariah looks up and sighs."
    "Finalmente vencida, Mariah levanta la vista y suspira."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:904
translate spanish hwb_s34_327e45bc:

    # Mariah "I guess we can probably pawn it off somewhere."
    Mariah "Я думаю мы сможем его где-нибудь заложить."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:911
translate spanish hwb_s34_d248a202:

    # "She walks back to her motorhome, waving along the other two."
    "Camina de vuelta a su casa rodante, haciendo señas a los otros dos para que la sigan."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:913
translate spanish hwb_s34_c867bd87:

    # Mariah "C’mon. Let’s go."
    Mariah "Давайте, пора ехать."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:917
translate spanish hwb_s34_1d538209:

    # Joseph "Well, see you two ladies down the road."
    Joseph "Еще увидимся с вами на дороге, леди."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:922
translate spanish hwb_s34_3b4b6f72:

    # Mariah "God, I hope not."
    Mariah "Боже, надеюсь нет."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:956
translate spanish hwb_s34_d2216c27:

    # "Tess looks back and forth, then scurries over to Marina and gives a quick hug around her waist before following the other two."
    "Tess mira de un lado a otro, luego corre hacia Marina y le da un abrazo rápido alrededor de la cintura antes de seguir a las otras dos."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:966
translate spanish hwb_s34_6e4c246d:

    # Tess "Bye."
    Tess "Пока."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:981
translate spanish hwb_s34_7d83b3c7:

    # "And with that, they speed off, leaving a trail of property damage behind them as they beep their loud-ass horn into the distance."
    "Y con eso, se alejan a toda velocidad, dejando un rastro de daños a la propiedad mientras tocan su bocina escandalosa en la distancia."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:985
translate spanish hwb_s34_a7ebc0a6:

    # "Marina and I are left alone, the cab long gone."
    "Marina y yo nos quedamos solas, el taxi ya se ha ido."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:991
translate spanish hwb_s34_be196dc8:

    # "Between small spurts of laughter, we thumb away each other’s tears, just happy to be together again."
    "Entre pequeños estallidos de risa, nos secamos las lágrimas con los pulgares, felices de estar juntas de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:993
translate spanish hwb_s34_57ca0832:

    # Amber "Hey, let’s go pick up the motorhome."
    Amber "Пойдем в наш трейлер."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:995
translate spanish hwb_s34_07cc638e:

    # Marina "Yeah."
    Marina "Пошли."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:1002
translate spanish hwb_s34_649f0b60:

    # "She sniffs one last time."
    "Ella solloza una última vez."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:1004
translate spanish hwb_s34_bdf8e21e:

    # Marina "I’d like that."
    Marina "Я была бы рада."

# game/script/hwb_s34.rpy:582
translate spanish hwb_s34_41c81653:

    # "It’s always the sane ones who die first."
    "Siempre mueren primero los cuerdos."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s34.rpy:109
    old "Running to Mariah's RV"
    new "Running to Mariah's RV"

